## Quick Reference

### Estimation

**Story Points (Fibonacci):**
```
1 - Trivial (< 1 hour)
2 - Simple (1-2 hours)
3 - Small (half day)
5 - Medium (1 day)
8 - Large (2-3 days)
13 - X-Large (1 week)
```

**T-shirt Sizing:**
```
XS - Quick fix, config change
S  - Small feature, bug fix
M  - Medium feature, integration
L  - Large feature, refactor
XL - Epic, major feature
```

### Risk Matrix

```
Impact x Probability = Priority

High Impact + High Probability = CRITICAL
High Impact + Low Probability  = HIGH
Low Impact + High Probability  = MEDIUM
Low Impact + Low Probability   = LOW
```

